# Local automation + coordination state (never commit)
.context/

# Per-project planning/tasking scratch files (never commit)
**/plan.md
**/tasks.md
**/todo.md

# Local prompt/catalog/lessons files (never commit)
**/prompt.md
**/problems.md
**/lessons.md

# Python cache artifacts
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
*.pyc

# Local virtualenvs (regenerated via `make venv`).
.venv/
venv/

# Editable-install metadata (regenerated on `pip install -e .`)
**/*.egg-info/

# Vendored model weights (audit-final §1.14). Fetch via ``make download-models``
# rather than committing to the repo.
model_cache/
**/*.safetensors
**/*.bin

# Regeneratable release archives (audit-final §1.14). Build via
# ``make external-packet`` or attach to a GitHub Release rather than commit.
holdout/external_partner_packet.zip
holdout/external_partner_packet/

# Security-sensitive (audit-3 §D10). Authoring an attestation, signing keys,
# institutional credentials, or partner API keys must never enter the repo.
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.pfx
.DS_Store


# Locally-rendered docs site (regenerable via `mkdocs build`).
# Excluded from git to prevent committing stale anonymisation state
# (see latest_opus_audit.md §P2-A.2).
site_build/
automechinterp_supplementary.tar.gz
Submission/

# Pre-submission audit + prompt scratch files (never commit)
*PREFLIGHT*.md
*preflight*.md
*audit*.md
*AUDIT*.md
hoursleft_*.md
final_lastminute_*.md
truefinal_lastminute_*.md

# Generated submission archives
automechinterp-ed-main.zip
supplementary.tar.gz
